g.text: Waiting for celery task to start
(pass executor TTL to deal with zombie executors)
Always-on executors need a couple of seconds here too
this is only for small images, large job
images must be preloaded somewhere else
if image is preloaded, this will exit quickly
It's important for both parties to start the deadline timer right here.
In practice, the validator will start its timer a bit later than executor - this is good,
as the validator is then less likely to time out before the executor. (unless the executor is dead)
